bits_fields.info:
Control timer 1 channel 1 selection 
1: Select internal LSI clock; 
0: Select external pins.

bits_fields.description:
Remap bit for ADC external trigger rule conversion.
1: ADC external trigger rule conversion connected to PC2;
0: ADC external trigger rule conversion connected to PD3.

Remap bit for ADC external trigger rule conversion.
1: ADC external trigger rule conversion connected to PC2;
0: ADC external trigger rule conversion connected to PD3.

Pin PA1 & PA2 remapping bit, this bit can be read or written by user. It controls the proper function of PA1 and PA2 (set to 1 when connected to an external crystal pin)
1: No functional role for pins;
0: Pin is used as GPIO and multiplexed function.
